asing effects. Thus, tracing circular dichroism in\ntime-resolve photoemission provides new insights into transient topological\nproperties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Mar 2020 20:40:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-28"}
