 accuracy\nand cost, limiting the finite basis set errors to less than 1kJ/mol.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Mar 2020 00:56:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Jun 2020 23:20:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-26"}
